  "prompt": "Where do I get all episodes of dragon ball Kai in English?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, you can find all episodes of \"Dragon Ball Kai\" (also known as \"Dragon Ball Z Kai\") in English through the following platforms:\n\n### 1. **Streaming Services**\n   - **Funimation**: This is the official streaming platform for *Dragon Ball Kai* in English. You can watch all episodes with the original English dub. Funimation offers both subtitled and dubbed versions.\n   - **Crunchyroll**: After the merger of Funimation and Crunchyroll, some *Dragon Ball Kai* content may be available here as well.\n   - **Hulu**: Hulu may have *Dragon Ball Kai* episodes available for streaming, depending on your region.\n\n### 2. **Physical Media**\n   - **DVD/Blu-ray**: You can purchase the complete series of *Dragon Ball Kai* on DVD or Blu-ray from retailers like Amazon, Best Buy, or directly from Funimation's store. This is a great option if you prefer owning a physical copy.\n\n### 3. **Digital Purchase**\n   - **iTunes**, **Google Play**, or **Amazon Prime Video**: You can buy individual episodes or full seasons of *Dragon Ball Kai* on these platforms.\n\n### 4. **Cable/On-Demand**\n   - **Toonami**: If it's airing in your region, you may be able to watch *Dragon Ball Kai* on the Toonami channel (part of Cartoon Network).\n\n### Note:\nMake sure to check availability in your region, as some streaming services or platforms may have restrictions based on your location. Additionally, \"Dragon Ball Kai\" is an edited and remastered version of *Dragon Ball Z*, so it has fewer episodes and removes most of the filler content.\n\nLet me know if you'd like more specific details!",
